fr.enseeiht.danck.voice_analyzer

Class VoiceAnalyzer

  • java.lang.Object
    • fr.enseeiht.danck.voice_analyzer.VoiceAnalyzer
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    VoiceAnalyzerMulti

    public class VoiceAnalyzer
extends java.lang.Object
    The main class responsible for coordinating all classes related to the signal process and analyze. Has two operating modes represented by the two methods "record" and "nextOrder". The first stores a unique Voice Field in database. The second interprets a series of Fields in order to generate a MetaOrder.
    Author:
    Anaël Megna, Kilian Boulhaïs, Cyrius Nugier
